<!--
### Anchor Help ###
0 = none
1 = Top
2 = Bottom
4 = Left
8 = Right

Can be combined by adding values. For example, the standard TopLeft anchor would
be anchor code 5.

### FontStyle Help ###
0 = Regular
1 = Bold
2 = Italic
4 = Underline
8 = Strikeout

Can be combined by adding values. For example, bold and underlined would be
fontstyle code 5.
-->

